nd all \nthe bones in my neck and spine were broken.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1901", "off": 4571, "word": "wouldn't believe", "class": "I_STATE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1902", "off": 4602, "word": "whistles", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1903", "off": 4620, "word": "fell", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1904", "off": 4644, "word": "could hardly get up", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1905", "off": 4721, "word": "were broken", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "3743", "off": 4736, "word": "\"Oho! You see, you're not so strong, imp. Go and take my iron club that's in \nthe rushes and try this: see who can throw it higher into the air.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1906", "off": 4746, "word": "see", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1907", "off": 4754, "word": "'re not so strong", "class": "STATE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1908", "off": 4778, "word": "Go", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1909", "off": 4785, "word": "take", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1910", "off": 4807, "word": "'s in \nthe rushes", "class": "STATE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1911", "off": 4829, "word": "try", "class": "I_ACTION", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1912", "off": 4839, "word": "see", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1913", "off": 4847, "word": "can throw", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1914", "off": 4890, "word": "took", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1915", "off": 4905, "word": "put", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1916", "off": 4933, "word": "set off", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "3744", "off": 4957, "word": "\"Well, Shabarsha, grandfather has ordered us to try one last time. Who can \nthrow this club higher into the air?\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1917", "off": 4987, "word": "has ordered", "class": "I_ACTION", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "PERFECT"}, {"id": "1918", "off": 5002, "word": "to try", "class": "I_ACTION", "tense": "INFINITIVE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1919", "off": 5028, "word": "can \nthrow", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "3745", "off": 5072, "word": "\"You throw it first and I'll watch.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1920", "off": 5077, "word": "throw", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1921", "off": 5097, "word": "'ll watch", "class": "PERCEPTION", "tense": "FUTURE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1922", "off": 5120, "word": "threw", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1923", "off": 5142, "word": "flew", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1924", "off": 5174, "word": "was just a \nblack dot", "class": "STATE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1925", "off": 5213, "word": "waited", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1926", "off": 5239, "word": "to come back", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "INFINITIVE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1927", "off": 5278, "word": "took", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1928", "off": 5311, "word": "stood", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1929", "off": 5346, "word": "leaned", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1930", "off": 5378, "word": "began", "class": "ASPECTUAL", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1931", "off": 5384, "word": "gazing", "class": "PERCEPTION", "tense": "PRESPART", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1932", "off": 5408, "word": "don't you \nthrow", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1933", "off": 5434, "word": "are you waiting", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "PROGRESSIVE"}, {"id": "1934", "off": 5456, "word": "asked", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "3746", "off": 5472, "word": "\"I'm waiting until that little cloud comes up, and then I'll throw this club \nat it. My brother, the blacksmith, is sitting up there and he can use this \niron in his business.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1935", "off": 5474, "word": "'m waiting", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "PROGRESSIVE"}, {"id": "1936", "off": 5509, "word": "comes", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1937", "off": 5529, "word": "'ll throw", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "FUTURE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1938", "off": 5585, "word": "is sitting", "class": "STATE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "PROGRESSIVE"}, {"id": "1939", "off": 5612, "word": "can use", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "3747", "off": 5650, "word": "\"Oh, no, Shabarsha! Don't throw that club into the cloud or else grandfather \nwill be angry.\"", "class": "REPORTING", "tense": "NONE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1940", "off": 5670, "word": "Don't throw", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PRESENT", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1941", "off": 5728, "word": "will be angry", "class": "STATE", "tense": "FUTURE", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1942", "off": 5754, "word": "grabbed", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1943", "off": 5775, "word": "dove", "class": "OCCURRENCE", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1944", "off": 5822, "word": "heard", "class": "PERCEPTION", "tense": "PAST", "aspect": "NONE"}, {"id": "1945", "off": 5861, "word": "